    "description": "幸存者联盟是一款结合了僵尸和肉鸽元素的类幸存者游戏，在丧尸横行的世界里玩家扮演一名人类幸存者对抗丧尸。通过击杀僵尸升级，选择合适的技能和物品来让自己生存下去。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>病毒已在全球蔓延，但人类远未放弃。直面恐惧，化作守护人类的战士，将丧尸们击退。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>升级战斗升级强化你的武器，改变武器的形态，用更强大的武器击败僵尸们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在游戏过程中你会遇到来自基地的补给品，里面随机出现一些强力道具。有一些能够强化你的枪械武器，有一些则能提升生存能力。合理选择他们是你变得更强的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在对战过程中遇到不同的幸存者，你可以邀请他们加入队伍，也可以将他们送回安全区从而获得奖励。根据你的喜好组建不同风格的队伍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过永久升级打造你喜欢的小队。决定你的升级方向，追求你最喜欢的职业，针对性升级从而成为世界的守护者。",
